{"tid":1192821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔。好。被。大。台。騎。劫","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T16:37:32.000Z","uid":50502,"like":955,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"8efcddef9c452b28194cec19a7da5d9b8230dcea","tid":1192821,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"黎緊幾日實有大台叫你和平散水　邊個衝就係鬼,控制你地一齊批鬥　叫你一齊唱歌宣示和平<br />\n但！記！住！<br />\n你就係你 唔需要被大台控制 覺得岩就做 唔岩就唔跟<br />\n亦唔需要指責其他人太和平/太暴力<br />\n沒人代表到你<br />\n<strong>記住自己為咩出黎</strong>"},{"pid":"ce5f6f3fbf886092d548d25264e65893d194e336","tid":1192821,"uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"絕對同意"},{"pid":"fb029effd76650167d88293f6acf3dbd42d917fa","tid":1192821,"uid":41389,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過70次/禁70次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備時項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待明天遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"867dfe67e51a64fa50663529d7f5f96e0b4cf2d4","tid":1192821,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"833ce49428dbb61ed39060a48abfbfe34408dda5","tid":1192821,"uid":148987,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"提防糾察篤灰散水"},{"pid":"990246058ca14bf325b655caf8aafde874d6e021","tid":1192821,"uid":148987,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"867dfe67e51a64fa50663529d7f5f96e0b4cf2d4","tid":1192821,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:30:57.000Z","msg":"小心黑警<br />\n切勿相認"},{"pid":"2767675d4b20ad9d484005ce6e4f9d3bbb5f75ef","tid":1192821,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:35:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid